      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a lovely finish with only minor surface scratches and a few tiny stone chips on the hood from normal highway use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, featuring well-preserved upholstery and fully functional electronics. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a solid service history; however, prospective buyers should note that the tires have about 40% tread remaining and will likely need replacement within the next year. It is a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next chapter.",
